content.rendered:
Directed by Annant Jaaitpaal.

Written by Shekhar Ramesh Mishra. Shekhar Ramesh Mishra. Shekhar Ramesh Mishra. Shekhar Ramesh Mishra.

Cast Pankaj Tripathi(Chuttan Shukla). Rahul Bagga(Harsh). Anupriya Goenka(Naina). Mouli Ganguly(CBI Inspector Mrinal Verma). Zakir Hussain(Kripashankar Shukla). Sadh Orhan(Shiva Pandey). Rajesh Sharma(Din Dayal Shukla). Evelyn Sharma(Bindass Babli). Rahaao(Shiv Pandey) . Gyanendra Aheer(Hotel Receptionst). Akshat Ajay(Neha’s Husband). Himayat Ali(Harsh Boss). Arihant(Dindayal Shukla Henchman 1). Pankaj Berry(Harsh’s Father). Deepak(Tourist). Anil Dubey(Thakur Khattan Singh). Kuntal Dutta(Hospital Orphan Dabodyu Disposal). Farook(Dhabawala). Sharmila Goenka(Bua). Rohit Hansraj(Dindayal Shukla Henchman 2). Kunal Jaiswal(Ram). Amar Jha(Rally Member). Jyoti Joshi(Naina’s Mother). Vinita Joshi(Amrita). Mohammed Khan(Rikshaw Driver 3). Zafar Khan(Rikshaw Driver 2). Zafar Khan(Fisher Man). Jugal Kishor(Girja Prasad). Naresh Kumar(Kallu). Tarun Kumar(Raje Shukla). Kunal(Bus Counter Guy). Manish Mishra(Aasi Commissioer). Brij Mohan(Assi Police Inspector). Shivendra Mohan(Hotel Servant). Pratap(Kripashankar Pandey Henchman 4). 

Language Hindi.

Producers Divya Anand. Sanjay Anand. Nishant Pawar. Ashish Raje. Yogesh Singh.

Production Experion Movies. PVR Pictures.
